name: 2023 Asia Conference on Electronics Engineering
content: Publication: After a careful reviewing process, all accepted papers after proper registration and presentation, will be published into International Journal of Electrical and Electronic Engineering & Telecommunications (ISSN: 2319-2518; CiteScore in 2021: 2.7): http://www.ijeetc.com/, which will be indexed by Scopus Google Scholar, Crossref, Citefactor, etc.
